          <h2 class="title_gray">
           Mellon Seminar
          </h2>
          <p>
           The Mellon Seminar’s theme from 2017 to 2020 is “Migration and the Humanities.” From 2014 to 2017, the Seminar examined the interrelationship between violence and non-violence.
          </p>
          <a href="/events-archives?q=series-history/Andrew%20W.%20Mellon%20Foundation%20Seminar">
           View all events
          </a>
         </div>
         <div class="col-sm-4" id="home_seminars">
          <div class="region region-seminars-image">
           <section class="block block-views clearfix" id="block-views-homepage-seminars-image-block">
