          <h2 class="title_gray">
           Writers Speak
          </h2>
          <p>
           Writers Speak brings significant contemporary writers to speak on campus, with the intention of fostering literary conversation.
          </p>
          <a href="/events-archives?q=series-history/Writers%20Speak">
           View all events
          </a>
         </div>
