              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
           </section>
          </div>
          <h2 class="title_gray">
           The Environment Forum
          </h2>
          <p>
           The Environment Forum is dedicated to exploring new work in the arts and humanities that reframes or reimagines the relationship of humanity to the rest of nature.
          </p>
          <a href="/events-archives?q=series-history/The%20Environment%20Forum%20at%20the%20Mahindra%20Center">
           View all events
          </a>
